add_details

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_details -  This method adds the details for the given coin type into the current list.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_details(string word,
string hd_sht,
string tl_sht,
string hd_lng,
string tl_lng,
mixed composition,
string plural)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^word%^RESET%^ - the coin type the details are for
%^BOLD%^hd_sht%^RESET%^ - the heads side short
%^BOLD%^tl_sht%^RESET%^ - the tail side short
%^BOLD%^hd_lng%^RESET%^ - the head side long
%^BOLD%^tl_lnd%^RESET%^ - the tail side long
%^BOLD%^composition%^RESET%^ - the composition of the money
%^BOLD%^plural%^RESET%^ - the plural value of the object, if 0 then use default plural
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/nmoney_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds the details for the given coin type into the current
list.
.EP

